Crawford  (  1908–77 , born  Lucille le Sueur ), the British actress  Joan Collins  (  b. 1933 ), the American comedienne  Joan Rivers  (  b. 1933 ), and the West Indian pop singer  Joan Armatrading  (  b. 1950 )."],"variants":[{"name":"John","meanings":["As a boy's name this represents a revival of Middle English <i>Jan</i>, a by‐form of   John  , or an adoption of the common European form with this spelling. As a girl's name it is a short form of names such as   Janet   and   Janice ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Joan Denchworth was born about 1251, in Denchworth, Berkshire, England, United Kingdom. She married Almeric Fettiplace in 1277, in Denchworth, Berkshire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1297, at the age of 47."},"et":{"about 1251–1297":"umbes 1251–1297","1247–1317":"1247–1317","1278–1348":"1278–1348","1251–1297":"1251–1297","1348":"1348","1247":"1247","1278":"1278","1277":"1277","1297":"1297","1251":"1251","about 1278":"umbes 1278","about 1251":"umbes 1251","1317":"1317","Denchworth, Berkshire, England":"Denchworth, Berkshire, England"},"fi":{"about 1251–1297":"noin 1251–1297","1247–1317":"1247–1317","1278–1348":"1278–1348","1251–1297":"1251–1297","1348":"1348","1247":"1247","1278":"1278","1277":"1277","1297":"1297","1251":"1251","about 1278":"noin 1278","about 1251":"noin 1251","1317":"1317","Denchworth, Berkshire, England":"Denchworth, Berkshire, England"},"fr":{"about 1251–1297":"environ 1251–1297","1247–1317":"1247–1317","1278–1348":"1278–1348","1251–1297":"1251–1297","1348":"1348","1247":"1247","1278":"1278","1277":"1277","1297":"1297","1251":"1251","about 1278":"environ 1278","about 1251":"environ 1251","1317":"1317","Denchworth, Berkshire, England":"Denchworth, Berkshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Joan Denchworth est née environ 1251, à Denchworth, Berkshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a épousé Almeric Fettiplace en 1277, à Denchworth, Berkshire, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils. Elle est décédée en 1297, à l’âge de 